snippet.title: Shütshimi: Seriously Swole Trailer
snippet.description:
Video animated and edited by James Id  
Game by Neon Deity Games  
Published by Choice Provisions 

Shütshimi is a randomized shoot'em up about a muscle-bound fish with memory problems defending the seven seas. 

http://totallychoice.com
